title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

“These are not the habits of a president who would wield the line-item veto pen mercilously.” [From The San Bernardino Sun, 1 February 1985. Submitted by J.B. Lawrence, San Bernardino, California.]
